This paper is primarily focused on differential privacy, which is a topic in cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses data analysis and computation on encrypted data, which are topics in databases (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper proposes optimizations for computation on encrypted data, which is a topic in algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT).
